Cell

public Cell(int i,
            int j,
            int type,
            java.lang.String param,
            int did)
A Cell object is an element of the map (grass, water, rock, ...). Can be referred to as "tile" or even miswritten as "tale"

Parameters:
i - : the line index of the cell
j - : the column index of the cell
type - : the type of the cell (takable, blocking, warp, ...)
param - : An additional param, such as a property (frozen, unstable, healthy)
did - : the design of the cell (grass, rock, water, lava,...)
